		<summary lang="en_GB">NEC - PC-FX (Beetle PC-FX)</summary>
		<summary lang="es_ES">NEC - PC-FX (Beetle PC-FX)</summary>
		<summary lang="it_IT">NEC - PC-FX (Beetle PC-FX)</summary>
